{"meta":{"version":"121","folder":"EventFlowMsg","file":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead","chunk":0,"start":0,"count":29,"total":29},"rows":[{"id":10817,"index":0,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_000_b","CNzh":"好了，塞尔达。\n这里不会有人来的。","TWzh":"好了，薩爾達，\n這裡沒有人會來的。","JPja":"さあ ゼルダ\nここなら<Ruby={2:4}だれ>誰も<Ruby={2:2}こ>来ないわ","USen":"All right, Zelda. We are alone as you requested."},{"id":10818,"index":1,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_001_b","CNzh":"你到底有什么事要跟我说呢？","TWzh":"你有什麼事要特地找我商量呢？","JPja":"<Ruby={2:2}お>折り<Ruby={2:2}い>入っての<Ruby={4:8}そうだん>相談というのは なんなのですか？","USen":"What was it you wanted to discuss with me in private?"},{"id":10819,"index":2,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_002_ac","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10820,"index":3,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_002_c","CNzh":"真是愚蠢。","TWzh":"何等愚蠢之人。","JPja":"なんてバカな<Ruby={2:4}ひと>人","USen":"You are far too trusting."},{"id":10821,"index":4,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_004_d","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10822,"index":5,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_005_c","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10823,"index":6,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_006_b","CNzh":"哎呀……\n被你这种欺骗他人的人这么说……","TWzh":"哎呀……\n被欺騙他人並做出這種事的人這麼說……","JPja":"あら…\n<Ruby={2:4}ひと>人を<Ruby={2:4}だま>騙してこんな<Ruby={2:4}こと>事をする<Ruby={2:4}ひと>人に…","USen":"Oh my. I'm surprised to hear you say such a thing."},{"id":10824,"index":7,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_007_b","CNzh":"还真是令人吃惊啊。","TWzh":"讓我很意外呢。","JPja":"そんな<Ruby={2:4}ふう>風に<Ruby={2:2}い>言われるのは<Ruby={4:8}しんがい>心外だわ","USen":"That is quite out of character for the Zelda I know."},{"id":10825,"index":8,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_008_b","CNzh":"加侬多夫的……","TWzh":"這位加儂多夫的……","JPja":"ガノンドロフの…","USen":"But then you..."},{"id":10826,"index":9,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_009_b","CNzh":"提线木偶。","TWzh":"傀儡。","JPja":"<Ruby={2:6}あやつ>操り<Ruby={4:10}にんぎょう>人形さん","USen":"are a puppet of Ganondorf."},{"id":10827,"index":10,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_011_d","CNzh":"你难道以为……\n我们什么都没有察觉到吗？","TWzh":"難道你以為……\n我們什麼都沒發覺嗎？","JPja":"<Ruby={4:10}わたしたち>私達が <Ruby={2:4}なに>何も<Ruby={4:4}きづ>気付いていないと\n<Ruby={2:4}おも>思っていたの？","USen":"Did you really think we hadn't realized your deceit?"},{"id":10828,"index":11,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_012_aaac","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10829,"index":12,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_012_aab","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10830,"index":13,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_012_ac","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10831,"index":14,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_012_c","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10832,"index":15,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_013_b","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10833,"index":16,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_014_b","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10834,"index":17,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_015_c","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10835,"index":18,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_017_ab","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10836,"index":19,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_017_c","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10837,"index":20,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_018_bb","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10838,"index":21,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_018_d","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10839,"index":22,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_019_b","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10840,"index":23,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_020_b","CNzh":"索尼娅大人！！！","TWzh":"索尼婭大人！！！","JPja":"ソニア<Ruby={2:4}さま>様ッッ！！！","USen":"Your Majesty!"},{"id":10841,"index":24,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_021_b","CNzh":"索尼娅大人！","TWzh":"索尼婭大人！","JPja":"ソニア<Ruby={2:4}さま>様ッ！","USen":"Queen Sonia!"},{"id":10842,"index":25,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_022_b","CNzh":"索尼娅大人——！\n索尼娅大人——！！","TWzh":"索尼婭大人──！\n索尼婭大人──！！","JPja":"ソニア<Ruby={2:4}さま>様ーッ！\nソニア<Ruby={2:4}さま>様ーッ！！","USen":"Oh no! Queen Sonia! No!"},{"id":10843,"index":26,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_023_c","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":10844,"index":27,"key":"DmT_ZE_QueenDead_Text_022_c"